  <brief_title>The Effects of Including Almonds in a Weight Loss Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Including Almonds in an Energy-restricted Diet on Weight, Abdominal Fat Loss, Blood Pressure, and Cognitive Function</official_title>
  <sponsors>
