    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether inclusion of almonds in a weight loss
      regimen will augment the rate of weight loss, promote a greater fat mass/fat-free mass ratio
      of weight loss, improve blood pressure and ameliorate the post-lunch dip in cognitive
      function.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether inclusion of almonds in a weight loss
      regimen will augment the rate of weight loss, promote a greater fat mass/fat-free mass ratio
      of weight loss, improve blood pressure and ameliorate the post-lunch dip in cognitive
      function.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
